<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٩٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عن عطاء أنه كره الطيب <span class="c2">(عند)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> الإحرام <span class="c2">(و)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> قال: إن كان به شيء <span class="c2">(منه)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> فليغسله <span class="c2">(ولينقه)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
